txt.en: Defeated many armoured shadows at Matum Graz.
Matum Graz can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should defeat armoured shadows at Matum Graz.

The watch-post of Matum Graz overlooks the path to the tower of Barad-dûr. Within the shattered walls of Matum Graz, armoured shadows and many other dark things wait for the approach of battle. You should defeat any of the shade-inhabited armours you come across in Matum Graz.
You defeated many of the armoured shadows at the watch-post of Matum Graz. Your efforts to expel the darkness upon the Shadowfells will not go unnoticed... by friends or foe alike.
